// During Mars Festival all users will receive up to 12% Daily Rewards.
// Extra 1% Compound Bonus for every compound action
// 24 hrs Compound timer
// 36 hrs Cut-off timer
// 4 hours Withdraw cool down timer
// 7% Tax and 1% Mktg
